Basic Example

If you create an account, you can obtain an authorization token to make more than 50 calls in one day at https://www.quandl.com/account

library(Quandl)
# Quandl.auth("ENTER_AUTH_CODE_HERE")
# Download data
US.fertility <-  Quandl("WORLDBANK/USA_SP_DYN_TFRT_IN")
head(US.fertility)
##         Date  Value
## 1 2012-12-31 1.8805
## 2 2011-12-31 1.8945
## 3 2010-12-31 1.9310
## 4 2009-12-31 2.0020
## 5 2008-12-31 2.0720
## 6 2007-12-31 2.1200
plot(as.Date(US.fertility$Date), US.fertility$Value, type='l', xlab="Date", 
     ylab="Fertility Rate", main="US Fertility Rate")
